info.author: Amy Suneeth, Martin Vladimirov, Andrea Tosheva, Kacper Janczyk, Rebecca Borski
info.name: emotion_detective
info.summary: This package provides functions to analyze emotions in video or audio files. It offers a comprehensive set of tools to detect and analyze emotions at a sentence level, producing valuable insights into the emotional content of multimedia sources.
